  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this registry is to determine the long term outcomes of heart
      transplantations performed at the Semmelweis University Heart and Vascular Center. All
      eventual interventional and non-interventional procedures will be accounted for and
      summarized.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
